content.text: The visualization provides: - Particle Distribution: Each particle represented as a point in 3D space - Color Coding: Particles colored by entropy level (viridis colormap) - Attractor Markers: Large X markers showing attractor positions - Interactive Controls: Rotate, zoom, and pan the 3D plot - Axis Labels: Clear labeling of determinacy, stability, and entropy axes
